msgid ""
"At least one mode of operation and information retrieval that does not "
"require visual acuity greater than 20/70 shall be provided in audio and "
"enlarged print output working together or independently, or support for "
"Assistive Technology used by people who are visually impaired shall be "
"provided."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/overview/vpat.rst:486
msgid ""
"**Remarks and Explanations**: Increasing Zoom level in Mattermost web app"
" can be used to fulfill this requirement."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/overview/vpat.rst:488
msgid ""
"At least one mode of operation and information retrieval that does not "
"require user hearing shall be provided, or support for Assistive "
"Technology used by people who are deaf or hard of hearing shall be "
"provided"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/overview/vpat.rst:492 ../../source/overview/vpat.rst:498
msgid ""
"**Remarks and Explanations**: There is no functionality relying on audio "
"only."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/overview/vpat.rst:494
msgid ""
"Where audio information is important for the use of a product, at least "
"one mode of operation and information retrieval shall be provided in an "
"enhanced auditory fashion, or support for assistive hearing devices shall"
" be provided."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/overview/vpat.rst:500
msgid ""
"At least one mode of operation and information retrieval that does not "
"require user speech shall be provided, or support for Assistive "
"Technology used by people with disabilities shall be provided."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/overview/vpat.rst:504
msgid "**Remarks and Explanations**: No speech-only interfaces in Mattermost."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/overview/vpat.rst:506
